Current default is Makefile.mpi_gfortran and Makefile.lammps.gfortran

from src folder-
```
make lib-milady
make lib-milady args="-m mpi_gfortran -e gfortran" # default, same as above
make lib-milady args="-m mpi_ifort -e ifort" # same as above
make lib-milady args="-m mpi_intel -e intel" # same as above
```
